ags:resource.dc:title: Method to estimate catches based on the Observers on board information
ags:resource.dc:description: The aim of this document is to present the method used in the period 2004-2010 to estimate the Spanish catch by species based in the information collecting by the “NAFO Observers” and the “Spanish Scientific Observers”.
ags:resource.dc:identifier: González-Costas, F. 2013. Method to estimate catches based on the Observers on board information. NAFO Sci. Coun. Res. Doc. 13/052, Serial Nº N6211: 5p.
